  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Left interscalene block has a different effect on heart's autonomic nervous system,
      compared to Right interscalene block. This effect is evident on the occurrence of
      bradycardia and hypotension during shoulder surgery in the beach chair position
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
